      "dialogAsk": "Oh! Careful, sweetpea — the sprinklers bite. I'm PATCHNURSE. Sticker for making it this far? Everyone gets a sticker. ...Listen. Down in that pit there's a little plush doll. The one that looks like HIM. I want it. Don't ask why. Fine — ask why: everything in here gets dropped eventually, and nobody ever gets picked back up. Bring him to me.",
